<span style="white-space:nowrap;"><i><a href="/wiki/Rushing_to_Paradise" title="Rushing to Paradise">Rushing to Paradise</a></i> (1994)</span> • <span style="white-space:nowrap;"><i><a href="/wiki/Cocaine_Nights" title="Cocaine Nights">Cocaine Nights</a></i> (1996)</span> • <span style="white-space:nowrap;"><i><a href="/wiki/Super-Cannes" title="Super-Cannes">Super-Cannes</a></i> (2000)</span> • <span style="white-space:nowrap;"><i><a href="/wiki/Millennium_People" title="Millennium People">Millennium People</a></i> (2003)</span> • <span style="white-space:nowrap;"><i><a href="/wiki/Kingdom_Come_(J._G._Ballard_novel)" title="Kingdom Come (J. G. Ballard novel)" class="mw-redirect">Kingdom Come</a></i> (2006)</span></p>
